      • storeMember

        public static boolean storeMember(Member member)
        Stores a member in the database. The member will not be stored if there's already a member with the same personal number in the database.
        Parameters:
        member - The member to be stored
        Returns:
        true if the member has been successfully stored, false otherwise.

      • checkPersonalNumber

        public static boolean checkPersonalNumber(java.lang.String personalNumber)
        Checks if a member can be stored in the database. A member can be stored in the database if there's not stored members with the same personal member (i.e database doesn't allow duplicate personal numbers).
        Parameters:
        personalNumber - The personal number to be checked
        Returns:
        true if the member can be stored in the database, false otherwise.

      • updateMemberBoatStorage

        public static boolean updateMemberBoatStorage(Member member)
        Stores the member's unstored boats. This method will only work if the member is already stored in the database.
        Parameters:
        member - Member whose boats list is to be updated
        Returns:
        true if the member has been found in the database and the boats list updated, false otherwise.
